    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for purchase is a driver-spec E46 M3, powered by the high-compression S54B32 powerplant featuring independent throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has undergone critical subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Performance-oriented maintenance includes a recent valve adjustment and a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator. While showing minor aesthetic patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
