    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road wear expected of a car that has been enjoyed. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats remain supple with no significant cracking, and all electronic components\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is sound, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and scheduled interval services. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly, providing a confident and comfortable driving experience. With a comprehensive service history and a smoke-free interior, this car offers a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking quality and reliability without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
