    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of love here and there, but overall it looks great and runs like a dream. If you're looking for a dependable car that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
