    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This example features critical preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS system service and rod bearing replacement to ensure the integrity of the reciprocating assembly. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates to address known structural stress points. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, sending power through a functional Variable M Differential Lock. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, and the cooling system has been updated for thermal efficiency. A true driver\u2019s car with crisp throttle response from its individual throttle bodies, this M3 is optimized for performance-oriented ownership.",
